Package: ggrm
Type: Package
Title: Remove Stuff From Ggplot
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Raphaël Scherrer
Maintainer: Raphaël Scherrer <raphael.scherrer@evobio.eu>
Description: This package provides wrapper functions to remove elements from
    a ggplot object (such as axes or facet strips) without having to call on 
    multiple functions (one for the ticks, one for the text, etc.).
License: GPL (>= 3)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.2.0
Imports: 
    ggplot2 (>= 3.4.2),
    purrr (>= 1.0.1),
    rlang (>= 1.1.0)
Suggests: 
    tibble (>= 3.2.1),
    patchwork (>= 1.1.2)
